title: Dan Snyder's Future, Bucs Or Rams Salvage Their Season?
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre, Kevin Clark, and Nate Tice! On today's show: How do you think Dan Snyder’s tenure as the owner of the Commanders plays out from here? Which road favorite are you more confident in: the Packers at -3.5 at the Lions, or the Chargers at -3 at the Falcons? How close should the Jets be to giving up on Zach Wilson? Plus, do you see the Rams or Bucs salvaging their season?
